desc.zh: 台州轨道交通，是服务于中国浙江省台州市的市域铁路系统，截止2022年12月台州共开通一条市域铁路线路，即台州S1号线
desc.en: Taizhou Rail Transit is a municipal railway system serving Taizhou,Zhejiang Province,China.Its first line,Taizhou Rail Transit,was opened on December 28,2022.

updateHistory.reason: As of December 2022 Taizhou Rail Transit has opened 1line of Taizhou Line S1
